room_title: Escape room "Escape from the Werewolf Village" by Two Bit Circus in Los Angeles
room_description:
So, you lost your way and wandered into a village where werewolves attack people every night. Bummer, right? The villagers start disappearing one by one, and soon enough the werewolves are after you. OH NOES

Can you reveal all the mysteries in time and escape the Werewolf Village? It’s a once in a lifetime, puzzle solving, mind-boggling adventure you’ll never forget (if you don’t die, that is).
